Package cs2030s.fp

Class Lazy<T>

java.lang.Object
cs2030s.fp.Lazy<T>
public class Lazy<T> extends Object
CS2030S Lab 6 AY22/23 Semester 2 Defines the Lazy Class which contains either a value which has already been calculated, or a producer which will produce the value when needed.
